<para id="fs-idm190448944"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 9B Explain the causes and effects of continuing policy debates about the role of the federal government over time</para>
<para id="fs-idm215377952"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Developments</emphasis>: 9.1.I.A, 9.1.I.B</para>
